The logging module in python everything you need to report the process and problems in your code 

purpose : record pogress and problems ...

Levels :  not set , Debug, Info, warning, Error, critical 
                               
                                                          
    (may be the numeric values are (0,  10,  20,  30,  40,  50 ))

